	quest.034B6B71E610D8E1.quest_desc: [
		"&oThe Blobbian is unique among organic life-forms, exhibiting no genetic variation between individuals... the only confirmed species is Blobbius Caelus, the Sky Blobbian..."
		"&o...lacking any sort of nervous system, all analysis shows no physical activity resembling thought. Yet Blobbius Caelus readily communicates, forms plans, and even makes specialized tools to navigate its environment..."
		"&o...have argued an extraphysical location for thought processing, or that Blobbius is part of a larger organism...&r"
		""
		"&8&o- Encyclopedia Daemonica&r"
	]
	quest.034B6B71E610D8E1.title: "Blobbius Caelus"
