	quest.2F51EA6259AD6A44.quest_desc: ["There is another form of construct, far more complex to use but highly versatile. The \"turtle\", a multipurpose robot build around a computer, can automate all sorts of tasks. If you never want to labor with those pitiful flesh hands again, making a turtle would help. You'll have to develop some sophisticated technology to even build one... unless a village might have one laying around?"]
