	quest.3B448BBF4352E4AB.quest_desc: ["The Casting Assistant Device is a versatile tool. Organic minds struggle to comprehend it, but when programmed correctly, it commands countless powers. Even the power to soar between the floating isles. Start with a CAD Assembly, a Core, and a Socket. Then combine them in a CAD Assembler to produce the blessed technology."]
	quest.3B448BBF4352E4AB.title: "Let's Build A Gun"
