	quest.4FFA0F65FA89D867.quest_desc: [
		"To enter the Atomic age, you'll need Radaway, a synthetic fluid that dulls the effects of deadly radiation."
		""
		"Though there are alternative ways to farm the Glowing Mushrooms needed to make Radaway, one option is to manufacture them: brew Potions of Glowing and apply them to Brown Mushrooms. "
		""
		"But first you'll need to head into the Nether and grab some Nether Wart, for Awkward Potions."
	]
	quest.4FFA0F65FA89D867.quest_subtitle: "Contraption 19-1"
	quest.4FFA0F65FA89D867.title: "Glow in the Dark I"
	quest.5004B1CBC8BA874D.title: "its a tree :)"
	quest.503719738ECF7E47.title: "Mass Bullying"
	quest.50766CC48FB21D85.quest_desc: [
		"A long time ago the blobis lived in the dark place. blobos was bored cus its too crowded and pointy and theres no up and down. then the dirt got bored too and went way up. blobbi learned about up and became sky bolb B))"
		""
		"i also heard theres something called down that really hurts, but it doesn hurt blobbers. But blobbims still need stuff to go up. theres lots of up stuff but im gonna make a stick :D"
	]
	quest.50766CC48FB21D85.title: "sky blobbin B)"
	quest.50E2D6459F3D68C0.quest_desc: ["{cabin.quest.50E2D6459F3D68C0.description1}"]
	quest.50E2D6459F3D68C0.title: "{cabin.quest.50E2D6459F3D68C0.title}"
	quest.5181318DC4AAD768.quest_desc: [
		"The Cactoid histories have always recorded that their origins lie beyond this world. Traditional myths state that beings from the moon once created the Cactoids, long ago. But when the land rose from the sea, they suddenly disappeared. Lacking any other concrete information about these hypothetical beings, historians dub them \"Lunarians\"."
		""
		"If you could somehow make it to the moon, you could solve the mystery of the Cactoids once and for all. And if the Lunarians really do exist, you could send them a clear message... that their creations have surpassed them."
	]
	quest.5181318DC4AAD768.quest_subtitle: " If I met my creator, I'd punch him in the face"
	quest.5181318DC4AAD768.title: "The Makers"
