	quest.5943F8F91AA79D59.quest_desc: [
		"Like some other rare minerals, this world seems to lack natural reserves of Uranium. They're thought to have been depleted long long ago, in a time so ancient even the Daemons' logs don't speak of it."
		""
		"However, there may still be &ounnatural&r deposits, lying deep in irradiated caverns buried by eons. If such a bounty really does exist, it would be more than enough to supply the Molten Uranium you need..."
	]
	quest.5943F8F91AA79D59.title: "Lost Technology"
