	quest.7A3C54CE8AD783D4.quest_desc: [
		"The history of this world is shrouded in mystery, but two things are certain. An ancient cataclysm tore the land from the sea; and long before that, the critical elements for nuclear technology were already used up."
		""
		"But what if history followed a different path? What if there were a parallel world, where nobody was around to consume those precious resources... because their world had already ended?"
	]
	quest.7A3C54CE8AD783D4.title: "The End of the World"
	quest.7A99056A697C4CEC.quest_desc: ["Aparently theres a rock that can remmber experiences. Thatd be even better then having a brain cus a rock is cooler and i can show off to bolbis frends and stuff."]
